<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244399>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. A. Epeolus julliani Pérez, 1884 female, habitus in lateral view. The taxon had been synonymised with Epeolus transitorius Eversmann, 1852 by Bogusch & Hadrava (2018) but is now recognized as a distinct species based on the work of Le Divelec (2021b). B. E. julliani female, head in oblique view. Pictures by Paolo Rosa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

